name: Online form builder
tagline: online form builder plugin for creating stunning  web forms
body:
## Welcome to the Online form builder repository.
we are happy to share our main form builder core with you so you will be able to host it yourself and extend it based on your needs this [form builder](https://formtitan.com) is very flexible and packed with amazing features.
we worked on this online forms platform for more then 2 years, you will find it exciting!

### Form Designer 
Easy to use angular and jquery code that will enable a drag and drop interface, sections, and more then 40 type of elements.
for example : phone, address,full name, etc....

### Creating custom logic
easily create custom logic for yoru form, server side logic , client side logic and validations

### push notifications
integrated with many 3rd parties, and also got a nice zapier app, we will happy to clone it as well!

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with code, or want to ask a question, feel free to ping us!

hapy forms!
